data.description: Location is everything!!! Welcome to this beautiful condo on the 19th floor of the stylish and contemporary Twelve Centennial Park building with Boutique Hotel on property for your friends and family!! The unit is very spacious with amazing views of the city from the private balcony. The loft style open floor plan is great for entertaining. Inside is freshly painted and updated… the kitchen offers granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, new fixtures and hardware. Living room has floor to ceiling windows with custom blinds and door screen. The bedroom is a generous size and the closet is professionally designed to keep you organized. The en-suite bathroom is a great size and is also updated with new fixtures and hardware. The laundry closet has recently replaced washer/dryer that stays with the unit as well as shelving for organization. The unit comes with one designated garage parking space and the building offers visitors’ parking. The property is FHA approved. The building offers gated and secure parking garage, 24/7 concierge service, pool and sundeck with BBQ grills, fitness center, a business center, a theater room, a club room and coffee bar!! The building is centrally located to all of Atlanta’s attractions, entertainment, restaurants, supermarkets (Whole Foods and Publix), Emory Hospital, Marta, GA Tech, Atlanta’s AU Center and the domestic and international airports. This city lifestyle is live-shop-work at it’s best!!
